{"article_id":"U00Lys008AHoekbm","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The leaders of Venezuela and Nicaragua extended offers of asylum to Edward Snowden .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Bolivia , others offer Snowden asylum","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Bolivia on Saturday joined Nicaragua and Venezuela","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"in offering National Security Agency whistleblower Edward Snowden asylum ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Reuters reported .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"The country becomes the third left-leaning South American nation","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"to offer asylum to Snowden ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"who ' s believed to be in a diplomatic \" purgatory \" at Moscow ' s Sheremetyevo airport","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and has applied for asylum in 21 countries .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" I want to tell ... the Europeans and Americans","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that last night I was thinking","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that as a fair protest , I want to say","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"that now in fact we are going to give asylum to that American","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"who is being persecuted by his fellow Americans , \"","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Morales said during a visit to the town of Chipaya ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"according to Reuters .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"\" If we receive a legal request ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"we will grant asylum . \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Morales ' s plane last week was forced to reroute and land in Vienna over suspicions","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that Snowden was aboard","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"and headed to Bolivia .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"\" The United States is using its agent and the president","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"( of Bolivia )","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"to intimidate the whole region , \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Morales said then of his plane ' s diversion .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"\" As head of state , the government of the Bolivarian Republic of Venezuela decided to offer humanitarian asylum to the young American Edward Snowden","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"so that he can live","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"( without ) ... persecution from the empire , \"","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"President Nicolas Maduro said Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"according to the Associated Press .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Nicaraguan President Daniel Ortega said","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"he ' d be willing to extend the same offer to the 30-year-old ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"but adding","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"he would only do so","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"\" if circumstances allowed it . \"","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"\" We have the sovereign right","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to help a person","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"who felt remorse","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"after finding out","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"how the United States was using technology","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to spy on the whole world , and especially its European allies , \"","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"Ortega said .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Wikileaks announced earlier Friday via Twitter","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that Snowden has applied for asylum in six more countries .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Edward # Snowden has applied to another six countries for asylum .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"They will not be named at this time","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"due to attempted US interference.","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"- WikiLeaks","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"( @ wikileaks )","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"July 5 , 2013","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"The NSA whistleblower fled the U.S. for Hong Kong , and then Russia .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"The United States has suspended his passport .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Venezuela ' s move will further heighten tensions between Maduro ' s post-Hugo Chavez regime and the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"even with President Barack Obama saying last month","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"he wasn ' t going to be \" scrambling jets","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"to get a 29-year-old hacker . \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Russia ' s Vladimir Putin has said","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he has no plans","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"of turning Snowden over to the U.S .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The Russian president said","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"his government would grant the NSA leaker asylum ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"but only if he stopped leaking secret information .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Vice President Joe Biden asked Ecuadorian President Rafael Correa to turn down Snowden ' s asylum request last week .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Snowden had initially hoped for asylum in Ecuador ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"but those designs have since faded .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"\" He ' s under the care of the Russian authorities , \"","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Correa said in an interview with the Associated Press .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Wikileaks founder Julian Assange is still holed up in that country ' s London embassy","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"to avoid extradition to Sweden","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"over sexual assault charges .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":139,"left":71,"right":138,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":77,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":73,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":72,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":5,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":6,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":137,"left":109,"right":136,"relation":"elab